parameters:
General Galvez: "What do you want? You must be quite bold to summon me
like this."

Strategist Domdora: "I have received the report. Lord Galvez, it seems
you have failed again."
General Galvez: "Grr..."

Strategist Domdora: "Your excellent subordinates have all been
defeated by Pony-Celes."

Strategist Domdora: "What will you do? There really is no turning back
now."
General Galvez: "Silence, Domdora! Do you wish to die here?"
Strategist Domdora: "Do you understand why I called you here?"
General Galvez: "..."

Strategist Domdora: "Pony-Celes grows stronger with each passing day.
Having dispatched four of our monsters, she has now become the
greatest threat to Zaida-G."

Strategist Domdora: "Perhaps she has even gained power surpassing
yours."
General Galvez: "..."

Strategist Domdora: "The annihilation of Pony-Celes is our sole
focus."

Strategist Domdora: "Even we, who are like cats and dogs, share this
common goal, do we not?"
Strategist Domdora: "How about it? Shall I lend you a hand?"

General Galvez: "Don't make me say it again, I need none of your
help!"
Strategist Domdora: "Think carefully, Lord Galvez."

Strategist Domdora: "We must risk our lives to protect our absolute
ruler, Lord Darg-Noa."

Strategist Domdora: "If you were to be defeated, Pony-Celes' fangs
could very well reach Lord Darg-Noa."

Strategist Domdora: "Joining forces to ensure the certain demise of
Pony-Celes seems to be the best course of action."

Strategist Domdora: "Besides, the fact that you came to meet me in
response to my call suggests that somewhere inside, you wish to borrow
my wisdom, does it not?"
General Galvez: "Grr..."
General Galvez: "Understood... Speak then."
Strategist Domdora: "Foh foh foh! At last, you've come around."

Strategist Domdora: "The strategy is quite simple. We lure Pony-Celes
to the central district of Urban Area."

Strategist Domdora: "You will deploy all your available forces to that
location."

Strategist Domdora: "If you engage Pony-Celes and win, our objective
is achieved."

Strategist Domdora: "Should you find yourself in a tough battle, at
that moment we will use the bombs buried underground to obliterate
Pony-Celes along with all combatants."

Strategist Domdora: "With the powerful bombs I secretly completed in
the basement of Saionji Pharmaceuticals."

Strategist Domdora: "Given the battle with you, Pony-Celes will surely
be exhausted. It will be nearly impossible for her to avoid the
bombs."

Strategist Domdora: "Either way, Pony-Celes will die. That's the
plan."

Strategist Domdora: "Ah, don't worry. Before activating the detonation
switch, I will ensure that you alone are safely evacuated."
General Galvez: "..."
General Galvez: "...Understood"

General Galvez: "I dislike it, but just this once I'll go along with
your proposal."

General Galvez: "I shall now mobilize all my forces to bury Pony-
Celes. Inform Lord Darg-Noa!"
Strategist Domdora: "I am looking forward to it, Lord Galvez."

Strategist Domdora: "The plan is finally coming to a head... Foh foh
foh!"
Would you like to save the data up to this point?
Yes
